## PROJECT IDENTITY

This is KMSAR — the Knowledge Management System for Academic Research at
Angeles University Foundation (AUF). It is a Laravel 11 MVC web application
with server-rendered Blade templates. It is NOT a SPA. Do not suggest React,
Vue, Next.js, or any client-side framework.

The system manages the full research lifecycle:
- Faculty register and update research records
- College Deans endorse or return submissions
- OVPRI/CDAIC administrators give final approval
- Filtered reports are generated as PDF and Excel

