## STACK RULES — ALWAYS FOLLOW

### PHP / Laravel
- PHP version: 8.3 — use modern PHP (readonly properties, enums, named args, match)
- Laravel version: 11 — use current conventions (no legacy patterns)
- Always use Eloquent ORM. Never write raw SQL strings with string interpolation.
- Always use Form Requests for validation — never validate in controllers directly
- Business logic belongs in Service classes under `app/Services/` — keep controllers thin
- All multi-step operations (approval + audit + notification) must be wrapped in DB::transaction()
- Always soft delete research records and documents — never hard delete in normal flows
- Use Gates and Policies for all authorization — never check roles inline in controllers
- Dispatch async Jobs for: file virus scanning, report generation, email notifications
- Queue driver: database (local/dev), redis (production)
- All routes must be named — always use `route()` helper, never hardcoded URLs
- Use `config('kmsar.xxx')` for app-specific constants — never hardcode values in logic

### Blade Templates
- All pages extend `layouts.app` — never build a standalone HTML page without the layout
- Use Blade components for all UI: `<x-button>`, `<x-badge>`, `<x-card>`, `<x-alert>`, `<x-modal>`
- Use Alpine.js for all interactivity — tabs, modals, dropdowns, SDG chips, form steppers
- Never use jQuery — Alpine.js only
- Chart.js 4 for all data visualizations — initialize in Blade view scripts, not separate JS files
- Always use `{{ }}` for output — never `{!! !!}` unless explicitly sanitized
- Flash messages use `session('success')`, `session('error')` patterns
- Use `@stack('modals')` in `layouts/app.blade.php` for modal portal

### CSS / Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes as the primary styling method
- For semantic, reusable component classes, use KMSAR.css (located at `public/css/KMSAR.css`)
- Link KMSAR.css in the layout: `<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/KMSAR.css') }}">`
- Use KMSAR.css class names with the `kmsar-` prefix for component classes:
  - Layout: `kmsar-app`, `kmsar-sidebar`, `kmsar-navbar`, `kmsar-main-content`, `kmsar-page-container`
  - Components: `kmsar-btn`, `kmsar-badge`, `kmsar-card`, `kmsar-alert`, `kmsar-modal`
  - Forms: `kmsar-input`, `kmsar-select`, `kmsar-textarea`, `kmsar-sdg-chip`
  - Tables: `kmsar-table`, `kmsar-table-wrap`
  - Charts: `kmsar-chart-card`, `kmsar-chart-canvas-wrap`, `kmsar-chart-legend`
- Color values to use (match the design system exactly):
  - Primary: `#1E3A8A`  (navy blue)
  - Primary hover: `#1E40AF`
  - Gold accent: `#D4AF37`  (use sparingly — reference numbers, badges, gold CTAs)
  - Background: `#F8FAFC`
  - Card: `#FFFFFF`
  - Border: `#E2E8F0`
  - Success: `#059669`
  - Warning: `#D97706`
  - Danger: `#DC2626`
  - Revision/info: `#2563EB`
- Never use inline `style=""` for colors — use Tailwind classes or KMSAR.css classes
- No emojis in UI — use SVG icons only (Heroicons style, stroke, not filled)
- No playful or casual design elements — institutional, clean, minimal

