## NAMING CONVENTIONS

### PHP
- Controllers: `PascalCase` + `Controller` suffix — e.g. `ResearchController`
- Services: `PascalCase` + `Service` suffix — e.g. `ApprovalService`
- Jobs: `PascalCase` + `Job` suffix — e.g. `FileVirusScanJob`
- Policies: `PascalCase` + `Policy` suffix — e.g. `ResearchPolicy`
- Form Requests: descriptive + `Request` suffix — e.g. `StoreResearchRequest`
- Models: singular `PascalCase` — e.g. `Research`, `College`, `Approval`
- Methods: `camelCase` — e.g. `endorseResearch()`, `generateReport()`
- Variables: `camelCase` — e.g. `$motherCollege`, `$approvalStage`
- Constants: `SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE`

### Database
- Tables: `snake_case`, plural — e.g. `research`, `research_authors`, `audit_logs`
- Columns: `snake_case` — e.g. `mother_college_id`, `av_result`, `approval_stage`
- Foreign keys: `{table_singular}_id` — e.g. `college_id`, `research_id`
- Enum values: `snake_case` strings — e.g. `'dean_review'`, `'ovpri_review'`, `'published_scopus'`

### Blade
- View files: `kebab-case.blade.php` — e.g. `research-detail.blade.php`
- Component files: `kebab-case.blade.php` in `resources/views/components/`
- Component usage: `<x-component-name>` — e.g. `<x-page-header>`, `<x-stat-card>`

### Routes
- Named routes follow: `{module}.{action}` — e.g. `research.index`, `approval.endorse`, `ovpri.dashboard`
- Route parameters: `{camelCase}` — e.g. `{research}`, `{document}`

